From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Codex <codex@openai.com>
Date: Tue, 16 Jun 2026 13:05:00 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] misc: add Fruit Jam USB host PIO2 RX probes

Add bounded receive-side probes to the Fruit Jam USB host bridge.
The new in-token and get-device-8 commands keep the stack honest:
they expose raw RX bytes, PIO IRQ state, and result counters without
claiming HID enumeration/report support yet.

---
 drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c | 400 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 1 file changed, 390 insertions(+), 10 deletions(-)

--- a/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c
+++ b/drivers/misc/fruitjam_usbhost.c
